### First, login to get token
POST http://localhost:54955/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Save the token and replace YOUR_TOKEN below

### Add items to cart first
POST http://localhost:54955/api/cart/add/1?quantity=2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

POST http://localhost:54955/api/cart/add/2?quantity=1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Create Order
POST http://localhost:54955/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
    "shippingAddress": "123 Main St, New York, NY 10001",
    "billingAddress": "123 Main St, New York, NY 10001",
    "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
    "shippingMethod": "Express",
    "notes": "Please leave at front door"
}

### Get all my orders
GET http://localhost:54955/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Get order by ID (replace 1 with actual order ID)
GET http://localhost:54955/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Get order by order number
GET http://localhost:54955/api/orders/number/ORD-XXXXXXX
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Cancel order
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Admin: Get all orders (need ADMIN role)
GET http://localhost:54955/api/orders/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Admin: Update order status
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/orders/admin/1/status?status=CONFIRMED
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Admin: Update payment status
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/orders/admin/1/payment?paymentStatus=PAID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN

### Admin: Add tracking number
PUT http://localhost:54955/api/orders/admin/1/tracking?trackingNumber=1Z999AA10123456784
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN